    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka schedules power cuts of up to 3 hours for July 17 and July 18",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka will impose power cuts of up to 3 hours on July 18 and 19, Public Utilities Commission (PUCSL) Chairman Janaka Ratnayake said.",
        "Groups ABCDEFGHIJKLPQRSTUVW will have power cuts of 1 hour and 40 minutes during the day and 1 hour 20 minutes at night.",
        "Group CC will have a 2-hour 30-minute power cut from 6.00 am to 8.30 am.",
        "Groups MNOXYZ will have a 3-hour power cut from 5.30 am to 8.30 am.",
        "The state-run Ceylon Electricity Board said the supply interruption time and restoration time will be varied within 30 minutes as indicated above. (Colombo/ July 17/2022)"
      ],
